p: Muurolane sesquiterpene endoperoxide, 1,4-peroxy-5-hydroxy-muurol-6-ene ( 101) has been obtained from plant Illicium tsangii (family Schisandraceae) [ 188, 189, 190]. The peroxide called schisansphene A ( 102) was isolated from the plant Schisandra sphenanthera, also known as the magnolia berry [ 191].
